  前項之未遂犯罰之。\r\n    前二項情形，不得科以超過其特定犯罪所定最重本刑之刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPHM/109%2c%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4%2c3514%2c20201201%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,109,上訴,3514,20201201,1","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"上訴","JNO":"3514","JDATE":"20201201","JTITLE":"詐欺等"}